nazariya:
Flexbox (Flexible Box Layout) — elementlarni qator yoki ustun bo'yicha moslashuvchan joylashtirish tizimi. 2012-yildan boshlab zamonaviy layoutning asosi.

## Asosiy tushunchalar

**Flex Container** — `display: flex` qo'yilgan ota element.
**Flex Item** — Container ichidagi to'g'ridan-to'g'ri farzand elementlar.
**Main Axis** — asosiy o'q (standart: gorizontal).
**Cross Axis** — kesma o'q (standart: vertikal).

```css
.container {
  display: flex; /* yoki display: inline-flex */
}
```

## flex-direction
Elementlar joylashuv yo'nalishi:
```css
.container {
  flex-direction: row;            /* → chapdan o'ngga (standart) */
  flex-direction: row-reverse;    /* ← o'ngdan chapga */
  flex-direction: column;         /* ↓ yuqoridan pastga */
  flex-direction: column-reverse; /* ↑ pastdan yuqoriga */
}
```

## justify-content
Main axis bo'yicha elementlarni taqsimlash:
```css
.container {
  justify-content: flex-start;    /* chapga yig'ish (standart) */
  justify-content: flex-end;      /* o'ngga yig'ish */
  justify-content: center;        /* markazlashtirish */
  justify-content: space-between; /* orada teng bo'shliq, yon tomonda yo'q */
  justify-content: space-around;  /* har yon tomonda teng bo'shliq */
  justify-content: space-evenly;  /* barcha bo'shliqlar teng */
}
```

## align-items
Cross axis bo'yicha (vertikal) tekislash:
```css
.container {
  align-items: stretch;     /* cho'zib to'ldirish (standart) */
  align-items: flex-start;  /* yuqoriga */
  align-items: flex-end;    /* pastga */
  align-items: center;      /* markazga */
  align-items: baseline;    /* matn bazalinasiga */
}
```

## Markazlashtirish (klassik muammo yechimi)
```css
.centered {
  display: flex;
  justify-content: center; /* gorizontal */
  align-items: center;     /* vertikal */
  min-height: 100vh;       /* balandlikni belgilash kerak */
}
```

## flex-wrap
Elementlar sig'masa nima bo'lishi:
```css
.container {
  flex-wrap: nowrap;       /* qatorni kesmasdan kichraytiradi (standart) */
  flex-wrap: wrap;         /* sig'masa keyingi qatorga o'tadi */
  flex-wrap: wrap-reverse; /* teskari tartibda qatorga o'tadi */
}
```

## gap
Elementlar orasidagi bo'shliq (margin ishlatmasdan):
```css
.container {
  gap: 16px;        /* barcha bo'shliqlar */
  gap: 10px 20px;   /* row-gap column-gap */
  row-gap: 10px;
  column-gap: 20px;
}
```

## Flex Item xususiyatlari

**flex-grow** — bo'sh joy bo'lganda elementning o'sish koeffitsienti:
```css
.item { flex-grow: 1; } /* Barcha bo'sh joyni to'ldiradi */
.item-big { flex-grow: 2; } /* Boshqalarga nisbatan 2 marta katta */
```

**flex-shrink** — joy kamaysa kichrayish koeffitsienti:
```css
.item { flex-shrink: 1; } /* Standart: kichrayadi */
.fixed { flex-shrink: 0; } /* Kichraymaydi */
```

**flex-basis** — elementning asosiy o'lchamini belgilash:
```css
.item { flex-basis: 200px; } /* Kamida 200px bo'ladi */
.item { flex-basis: 33.33%; } /* Uchta teng ustun */
```

**flex shorthand:**
```css
.item { flex: 1; }          /* flex: 1 1 0% */
.item { flex: 0 0 200px; }  /* o'smaydi, kichraymaydi, 200px */
.item { flex: 2 1 auto; }   /* grow:2, shrink:1, basis:auto */
```

**align-self** — bitta elementni boshqacha tekislash:
```css
.special { align-self: flex-end; }
```

**order** — elementlar tartibini o'zgartirish (HTML o'zgarmasdan):
```css
.first { order: -1; } /* Boshqa elementlar order: 0 standart */
.last { order: 1; }
```

## Amaliy misol — navigatsiya
```css
nav {
  display: flex;
  justify-content: space-between;
  align-items: center;
  padding: 0 24px;
  height: 64px;
  background: #1a1a2e;
}

.nav-links {
  display: flex;
  gap: 24px;
  list-style: none;
}

.nav-links a {
  color: white;
  text-decoration: none;
  transition: color 0.2s;
}

.nav-links a:hover { color: #6c63ff; }
```

## Karta Grid — flex-wrap bilan
```css
.cards {
  display: flex;
  flex-wrap: wrap;
  gap: 20px;
  padding: 20px;
}

.card {
  flex: 0 0 calc(33.33% - 14px); /* 3 ta ustun, gapni hisoblab */
  background: white;
  border-radius: 12px;
  padding: 20px;
}
```

topshiriq.yechim:
nav { display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center; background: #1a1a2e; padding: 0 32px; height: 64px; }
.logo { color: #6c63ff; font-size: 24px; font-weight: bold; }
.nav-links { display: flex; list-style: none; gap: 24px; }
.nav-links a { color: #ccc; text-decoration: none; }
.nav-links a:hover { color: white; }
.hero { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 40px; padding: 60px 32px; min-height: calc(100vh - 64px); }
.hero-text { flex: 1; }
.hero-text h1 { font-size: 40px; margin-bottom: 16px; color: #1a1a2e; }
.hero-text p { color: #666; margin-bottom: 24px; font-size: 18px; }
.hero-text button { background: #6c63ff; color: white; border: none; padding: 12px 32px; border-radius: 8px; font-size: 16px; cursor: pointer; }
.hero-image { flex: 1; }
.hero-image img { width: 100%; border-radius: 12px; }
@media (max-width: 600px) { .hero { flex-direction: column; } .nav-links { display: none; } }

nazariya:
CSS Grid Layout — ikki o'lchovli (2D) joylashtirish tizimi. Flexbox bir o'qda ishlasa, Grid ham qator (row), ham ustun (column) bo'yicha bir vaqtda boshqaradi.

## Grid asoslari

```css
.container {
  display: grid;
}
```

## grid-template-columns va grid-template-rows

```css
.container {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: 200px 200px 200px;  /* 3 ta 200px ustun */
  grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr 1fr;         /* 3 ta teng ustun */
  grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);       /* Yuqori bilan bir xil */
  grid-template-columns: 1fr 2fr 1fr;          /* nisbatli ustunlar */
  grid-template-columns: 200px 1fr;            /* Aralash */
  grid-template-rows: 100px auto 100px;        /* header, kontent, footer */
}
```

**fr birlik** — bo'sh joyni ulushga bo'ladi:
```css
/* 3 teng ustun: 1fr 1fr 1fr */
/* 25%-50%-25% ustunlar: 1fr 2fr 1fr */
```

## gap
```css
.container {
  gap: 20px;          /* qator va ustun bo'shliqlari */
  row-gap: 16px;
  column-gap: 24px;
}
```

## repeat() va minmax()
```css
.grid {
  /* Har bir ustun kamida 200px, bo'sh joy bo'lsa kengayadi */
  grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(200px, 1fr));

  /* Sig'gan qadar ustun, bo'sh qolmasin */
  grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(250px, 1fr));
}
```
auto-fill/auto-fit — responsive grid uchun juda kuchli!

## grid-column va grid-row — elementni joylashtirish

```css
.item {
  /* Grid chiziqlari bo'yicha joylashtirish */
  grid-column: 1 / 3;   /* 1-chiziqdan 3-chiziqqa = 2 ustun */
  grid-row: 1 / 2;      /* 1-2 qator orasida */

  /* span yordamida */
  grid-column: 1 / span 2;  /* 1-chiziqdan 2 ustun oladi */
  grid-column: span 3;      /* Hozirgi joydan 3 ustun oladi */
}
```

## grid-template-areas — vizual layout

Kompleks layoutlar uchun eng o'qilishi oson usul:
```css
.layout {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: 240px 1fr 300px;
  grid-template-rows: 64px 1fr 64px;
  grid-template-areas:
    "header header  header"
    "aside  main    aside2"
    "footer footer  footer";
  min-height: 100vh;
  gap: 0;
}

.header { grid-area: header; background: #1a1a2e; }
.sidebar { grid-area: aside; background: #f5f5f5; }
.main { grid-area: main; padding: 24px; }
.sidebar-right { grid-area: aside2; background: #f0f0f0; }
.footer { grid-area: footer; background: #1a1a2e; }
```

Har bir nom `grid-area` xususiyati bilan elementga biriktiriladi.

## Elementlarni tekislash

```css
.container {
  justify-items: start | center | end | stretch;   /* gorizontal */
  align-items: start | center | end | stretch;     /* vertikal */
  justify-content: start | center | end | space-between; /* grid o'zi */
  align-content: start | center | end | space-between;   /* grid o'zi */
}

/* Bitta element uchun */
.item {
  justify-self: center;
  align-self: end;
}
```

## place-items shorthand
```css
.container {
  place-items: center;         /* align-items: center; justify-items: center; */
  place-content: center start; /* align-content va justify-content */
}
```

## Amaliy misol — Foto Galereya
```css
.gallery {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(250px, 1fr));
  gap: 16px;
  padding: 24px;
}

.gallery-item {
  border-radius: 8px;
  overflow: hidden;
}

.gallery-item img {
  width: 100%;
  height: 200px;
  object-fit: cover;
  transition: transform 0.3s;
}

.gallery-item img:hover { transform: scale(1.05); }

/* Featured rasm: katta maydon */
.gallery-item:first-child {
  grid-column: span 2;
  grid-row: span 2;
}
.gallery-item:first-child img { height: 100%; }
```

## CSS Grid vs Flexbox qachon ishlatish
- **Grid** — ikki o'lchovli layout (qatorlar VA ustunlar bir vaqtda)
- **Flexbox** — bir o'lchovli (faqat qator yoki ustun)
- Ko'pincha ikkalasi birgalikda: Grid sahifa layouti, Flexbox ichki komponentlar uchun

topshiriq.yechim:
body { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 240px 1fr 200px; grid-template-rows: 60px 1fr 50px; grid-template-areas: 'header header header' 'sidebar main right' 'footer footer footer'; gap: 0; }
header { grid-area: header; background: #1a1a2e; color: white; display: flex; align-items: center; padding: 0 24px; font-size: 20px; font-weight: bold; }
.sidebar { grid-area: sidebar; background: #f5f5f5; padding: 20px; border-right: 1px solid #e0e0e0; }
main { grid-area: main; padding: 24px; }
.right-panel { grid-area: right; background: #f0f8ff; padding: 20px; border-left: 1px solid #e0e0e0; }
footer { grid-area: footer; background: #333; color: white; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; }
.cards { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(180px, 1fr)); gap: 16px; }
.card { background: white; border: 1px solid #e0e0e0; border-radius: 8px; padding: 20px; text-align: center; }

nazariya:
Responsive dizayn — sayt barcha ekran o'lchamlarda (telefon, planshet, kompyuter) yaxshi ko'rinishini ta'minlaydi. 2024-yilda mobil traff umumiy internetning 60%+ ni tashkil etadi.

## Viewport Meta Tegi

Har bir HTML sahifada bo'lishi shart:
```html
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
```
`width=device-width` — ekran kengligini qurilma kengligiga tenglashtiradi.
`initial-scale=1.0` — zoom darajasi boshlang'ichda 1.

## Media Query asoslari

```css
@media (condition) {
  /* Bu shart bajarilganda qo'llaniladigan stilllar */
}
```

**Keng ishlatiluvchi breakpointlar:**
```css
/* Extra kichik: telefon (< 576px) */
/* Kichik: katta telefon (>= 576px) */
@media (min-width: 576px) { ... }

/* O'rta: planshet (>= 768px) */
@media (min-width: 768px) { ... }

/* Katta: kichik kompyuter (>= 992px) */
@media (min-width: 992px) { ... }

/* Extra katta: (>= 1200px) */
@media (min-width: 1200px) { ... }
```

## Mobile-First Approach

**Mobile-first** — kichik ekran uchun avval yozib, katta ekran uchun qo'shimcha qilish:
```css
/* Asosiy stil — mobil uchun */
.container {
  flex-direction: column;
  padding: 16px;
}

/* Planshet va undan katta */
@media (min-width: 768px) {
  .container {
    flex-direction: row;
    padding: 24px;
  }
}

/* Katta ekran */
@media (min-width: 1200px) {
  .container {
    max-width: 1200px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 32px;
  }
}
```

**Desktop-first** (eski usul) — katta ekrandan boshlab, kichrayganda o'zgartirish:
```css
.container { flex-direction: row; } /* Asosiy */
@media (max-width: 768px) {
  .container { flex-direction: column; } /* Kichik ekranda o'zgartirish */
}
```

Sanoat standarti: **mobile-first** tavsiya etiladi.

## Responsive Birliklari

```css
/* Nisbiy birliklar */
.text { font-size: 1rem; }      /* 1rem = 16px (standart) */
.text { font-size: 1.5em; }     /* Ota elementning 1.5 barobari */
.box { width: 50%; }            /* Ota elementning 50% */

/* Viewport birliklar */
.hero { height: 100vh; }        /* Viewport balandligi 100% */
.hero { width: 100vw; }         /* Viewport kengligi 100% */
.text { font-size: 4vw; }       /* Viewport kengligiga bog'liq shrift */

/* DVH/SVH/LVH (2022-yildan) */
.hero { height: 100dvh; }       /* Dinamik viewport (mobil brauzerlarda to'g'ri) */
```

## Responsive Rasmlar
```css
img {
  max-width: 100%; /* Rasm konteynerdan chiqmasin */
  height: auto;    /* Nisbat saqlansin */
}

/* object-fit — rasm to'ldirishni boshqarish */
.card-img {
  width: 100%;
  height: 200px;
  object-fit: cover;   /* Kesiladi, nisbat saqlanadi */
  object-fit: contain; /* To'liq ko'rinadi, bo'sh joy qoladi */
  object-position: center top; /* Nima kesilishini belgilash */
}
```

## Responsive Tipografiya
```css
/* clamp(min, preferred, max) */
h1 {
  font-size: clamp(1.5rem, 5vw, 3rem);
  /* Min: 24px, max: 48px, ideal: ekran kengligining 5% */
}

p {
  font-size: clamp(1rem, 2vw, 1.25rem);
}
```

## CSS Custom Media Queries (O'zgaruvchilar)
```css
/* Ko'p ishlatiladigan breakpointlarni o'zgaruvchi sifatida saqlash */
:root {
  --mobile: 576px;
  --tablet: 768px;
  --desktop: 992px;
}
/* Lekin CSS hali @custom-media ni to'liq qo'llab-quvvatlamaydi — SCSS ishlatiladi */
```

## Responsive Nav — Hamburger Menu
```css
.hamburger { display: none; }
.nav-links { display: flex; gap: 24px; }

@media (max-width: 768px) {
  .hamburger { display: block; cursor: pointer; }
  .nav-links {
    display: none;
    flex-direction: column;
    position: absolute;
    top: 64px; left: 0; right: 0;
    background: #1a1a2e;
    padding: 16px;
  }
  .nav-links.open { display: flex; }
}
```

## print Media
```css
@media print {
  nav, .sidebar, button { display: none; }
  body { font-size: 12pt; color: black; }
  a::after { content: " (" attr(href) ")"; }
}
```

## prefers-color-scheme — Dark Mode
```css
:root {
  --bg: white;
  --text: #333;
}

@media (prefers-color-scheme: dark) {
  :root {
    --bg: #1a1a2e;
    --text: #f0f0f0;
  }
}

body { background: var(--bg); color: var(--text); }
```

topshiriq.yechim:
:root { --bg: #f5f5f5; --card-bg: white; --text: #333; --border: #e0e0e0; }
@media (prefers-color-scheme: dark) { :root { --bg: #0f0f1a; --card-bg: #1a1a2e; --text: #e0e0e0; --border: #333; } }
body { background: var(--bg); color: var(--text); padding: 16px; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; }
.container { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 16px; max-width: 1200px; margin: 0 auto; }
@media (min-width: 768px) { .container { grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr); gap: 20px; } }
@media (min-width: 1024px) { .container { grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr); } }
.card { background: var(--card-bg); border: 1px solid var(--border); border-radius: 12px; overflow: hidden; }
.card img { width: 100%; height: 200px; object-fit: cover; }
.card-body { padding: 16px; }
.card-body h3 { margin-bottom: 8px; font-size: clamp(1rem, 2.5vw, 1.25rem); }
.card-body p { color: #888; margin-bottom: 16px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.5; }
.card-body button { width: 100%; padding: 10px; background: #6c63ff; color: white; border: none; border-radius: 6px; cursor: pointer; }

nazariya:
CSS animatsiyalar sahifani jonli va interaktiv qiladi. JavaScript kabi murakkab kod yozmasdan ham chiroyli effektlar yaratsa bo'ladi.

## transition

Elementning bir holatdan ikkinchisiga o'tish animatsiyasi:
```css
.button {
  background: #6c63ff;
  transform: scale(1);
  transition: background 0.3s ease, transform 0.2s ease;
  /* xususiyat vaqt timing-function delay */
}

.button:hover {
  background: #5a52d5;
  transform: scale(1.05);
}
```

**transition sintaksisi:**
```css
transition: property duration timing-function delay;

/* Barcha o'zgaruvchi xususiyatlar uchun */
transition: all 0.3s ease;

/* Ko'p xususiyat */
transition: background 0.3s, transform 0.2s 0.1s;
/*                                          ↑ delay */
```

**Timing Functions:**
```css
transition: all 0.3s ease;         /* sekin-sekin tezlashadi, keyin sekinlashadi */
transition: all 0.3s linear;       /* bir xil tezlik */
transition: all 0.3s ease-in;      /* sekin boshlanadi */
transition: all 0.3s ease-out;     /* sekin tugaydi */
transition: all 0.3s ease-in-out;  /* ikkalasi */
transition: all 0.3s cubic-bezier(0.68, -0.55, 0.265, 1.55); /* bounce */
```

## transform

Elementni ko'chirish, aylantirish, kattalashtirish — **layout ta'sir qilmasdan:**
```css
.box {
  transform: translateX(50px);        /* Gorizontal ko'chirish */
  transform: translateY(-20px);        /* Vertikal ko'chirish */
  transform: translate(50px, -20px);   /* X va Y */
  transform: scale(1.5);              /* 1.5 barobar kattalashtirish */
  transform: scale(0.8, 1.2);         /* X va Y alohida */
  transform: rotate(45deg);           /* 45 gradus aylantirish */
  transform: rotate(-10deg);          /* Teskari */
  transform: skewX(20deg);            /* Qiya qilish */
  transform: skewY(10deg);

  /* Ko'p transformlar birga */
  transform: translateY(-4px) scale(1.02) rotate(2deg);
}

/* transform-origin — aylantirish markazi */
.logo {
  transform-origin: left center; /* Chap markazidan aylanadi */
  transform: rotate(5deg);
}
```

## @keyframes — Murakkab animatsiyalar

```css
/* Animatsiyani aniqlash */
@keyframes fadeIn {
  from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(20px); }
  to   { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
}

/* Foiz bilan */
@keyframes pulse {
  0%   { transform: scale(1); box-shadow: 0 0 0 0 rgba(108, 99, 255, 0.4); }
  70%  { transform: scale(1.05); box-shadow: 0 0 0 10px rgba(108, 99, 255, 0); }
  100% { transform: scale(1); box-shadow: 0 0 0 0 rgba(108, 99, 255, 0); }
}

@keyframes spin {
  from { transform: rotate(0deg); }
  to   { transform: rotate(360deg); }
}

@keyframes shimmer {
  0%   { background-position: -468px 0; }
  100% { background-position: 468px 0; }
}
```

**animation xususiyati:**
```css
.element {
  animation: fadeIn 0.5s ease-out forwards;
  /* nom   vaqt  timing  fill-mode */
}

/* To'liq sintaksis */
.loader {
  animation: spin 1s linear infinite;
  /* nom  vaqt  timing  takror-soni */
}

.badge {
  animation: pulse 2s ease-in-out infinite;
}

/* Ko'p animatsiya */
.card {
  animation: fadeIn 0.5s ease-out, pulse 3s ease-in-out 1s infinite;
}

/* animation-fill-mode */
.box {
  animation: fadeIn 1s ease forwards;  /* tugagandan keyin oxirgi holatda qoladi */
  animation: fadeIn 1s ease backwards; /* boshidan oldingi holat */
  animation: fadeIn 1s ease both;
}
```

## Amaliy misollar

**Loading Spinner:**
```css
@keyframes spin {
  to { transform: rotate(360deg); }
}

.spinner {
  width: 40px;
  height: 40px;
  border: 4px solid #f0f0f0;
  border-top-color: #6c63ff;
  border-radius: 50%;
  animation: spin 0.8s linear infinite;
}
```

**Skeleton Loading:**
```css
@keyframes shimmer {
  0% { background-position: -200% 0; }
  100% { background-position: 200% 0; }
}

.skeleton {
  background: linear-gradient(90deg, #f0f0f0 25%, #e8e8e8 50%, #f0f0f0 75%);
  background-size: 200% 100%;
  animation: shimmer 1.5s infinite;
  border-radius: 4px;
}
```

**Floating animatsiya:**
```css
@keyframes float {
  0%, 100% { transform: translateY(0); }
  50% { transform: translateY(-12px); }
}

.hero-icon { animation: float 3s ease-in-out infinite; }
```

## will-change — Ishlashni optimallashtirish
```css
.animated {
  will-change: transform, opacity; /* GPU da ishlaydi */
}
```

## prefers-reduced-motion
```css
@media (prefers-reduced-motion: reduce) {
  *, *::before, *::after {
    animation-duration: 0.01ms !important;
    transition-duration: 0.01ms !important;
  }
}
```

