CSS Custom Properties (O'zgaruvchilar) — CSS ning kuchli xususiyati bo'lib, qayta ishlatiladigan qiymatlarni saqlash va dinamik o'zgartirish imkonini beradi.

## CSS Custom Properties (--var)

```css
/* O'zgaruvchilarni aniqlash — :root global scope */
:root {
  --primary: #6c63ff;
  --secondary: #ff6b6b;
  --bg: #0f0f1a;
  --text: #e0e0e0;
  --card-bg: #1a1a2e;
  --border: rgba(255,255,255,0.1);

  --spacing-xs: 4px;
  --spacing-sm: 8px;
  --spacing-md: 16px;
  --spacing-lg: 24px;
  --spacing-xl: 32px;

  --radius-sm: 4px;
  --radius-md: 8px;
  --radius-lg: 16px;
  --radius-full: 9999px;

  --font-size-base: 1rem;
  --font-size-lg: 1.25rem;
  --font-size-xl: 1.5rem;
  --font-size-2xl: 2rem;
}

/* Ishlatish: var(--o'zgaruvchi-nomi) */
.button {
  background: var(--primary);
  color: white;
  padding: var(--spacing-md) var(--spacing-lg);
  border-radius: var(--radius-md);
}

/* Zaxira qiymat */
.card {
  background: var(--card-bg, white); /* Agar --card-bg aniqlanmagan bo'lsa white */
}
```

## Komponent ichida lokal o'zgaruvchilar
```css
.button {
  --btn-color: #6c63ff;
  --btn-hover: #5a52d5;
  background: var(--btn-color);
  transition: background 0.2s;
}

.button:hover { background: var(--btn-hover); }

/* Variantlar — faqat rang o'zgaruvchisini o'zgartirish */
.button.danger { --btn-color: #ff6b6b; --btn-hover: #e55a5a; }
.button.success { --btn-color: #51cf66; --btn-hover: #40b55a; }
```

## Dark Mode — o'zgaruvchilar bilan
```css
:root {
  --bg: #ffffff;
  --text: #1a1a1a;
  --card: #f5f5f5;
}

[data-theme="dark"], .dark {
  --bg: #0f0f1a;
  --text: #e0e0e0;
  --card: #1a1a2e;
}

body { background: var(--bg); color: var(--text); }
.card { background: var(--card); }
```
```javascript
// Dark mode toggle
btn.addEventListener('click', () => {
  document.body.classList.toggle('dark');
});
```

## calc() — Hisob-kitob
```css
/* Matematik hisoblash */
.sidebar { width: calc(100% - 300px); } /* Kenglikdan 300px olib tashlash */
.icon { width: calc(var(--spacing-md) * 2); } /* O'zgaruvchi bilan */
.hero { min-height: calc(100vh - 64px); } /* Header balandligini olib tashlash */
.grid-item { width: calc(33.33% - 16px); } /* Gap hisoblab */

/* Aralash birliklar */
.element {
  padding: calc(1rem + 2vw); /* rem va vw aralash */
  font-size: calc(14px + 0.5vw);
}
```

## clamp() — Responsive o'lchamlar
```css
/* clamp(minimum, preferred, maximum) */
h1 { font-size: clamp(1.5rem, 5vw, 3rem); }
p { font-size: clamp(0.875rem, 2vw, 1.125rem); }
.container { width: clamp(320px, 90%, 1200px); }
.card { padding: clamp(16px, 3vw, 32px); }

/* O'zgaruvchilar bilan */
:root {
  --fluid-h1: clamp(2rem, 4vw + 1rem, 4rem);
  --fluid-body: clamp(1rem, 1.5vw + 0.5rem, 1.25rem);
}
```

## min() va max()
```css
.container {
  width: min(100%, 1200px);  /* 100% va 1200px ning kichigi */
}

.image {
  height: max(200px, 30vw); /* 200px va 30vw ning kattasi */
}
```

## CSS Nesting (2023+)

Modern brauzerlar CSS Nesting ni to'liq qo'llab-quvvatlaydi (SCSS kerak emas):
```css
/* Oldin (SCSS kerak edi) */
.card { ... }
.card h2 { ... }
.card:hover { ... }

/* Endi native CSS Nesting */
.card {
  background: var(--card-bg);
  padding: var(--spacing-lg);
  border-radius: var(--radius-lg);

  /* Farzand element */
  h2 {
    font-size: var(--font-size-xl);
    margin-bottom: var(--spacing-sm);
  }

  p {
    color: #888;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  /* Psevdo-klass */
  &:hover {
    transform: translateY(-4px);
    box-shadow: 0 8px 24px rgba(0,0,0,0.2);
  }

  /* Modifikator klass */
  &.featured {
    border: 2px solid var(--primary);
  }

  /* Media query ichida */
  @media (min-width: 768px) {
    padding: var(--spacing-xl);
  }
}
```

