nazariya:
Sass (Syntactically Awesome Style Sheets) — CSS preprocessori bo'lib, CSS ga dasturlash tili xususiyatlarini qo'shadi. SCSS (Sassy CSS) — Sass ning CSS sintaksisiga o'xshash versiyasi.

## O'rnatish va ishlatish

```bash
# NPM orqali o'rnatish
npm install -g sass

# Compile qilish
sass style.scss style.css

# Watch mode (avtomatik compile)
sass --watch style.scss:style.css

# Papka kuzatish
sass --watch scss/:css/
```

## SCSS vs CSS Farqi

Fayllar `.scss` kengaymasi bilan saqlanadi va standart CSS ga compile qilinadi.

## Nesting

CSS dagi takroriy selectorlarni qisqartirish:
```scss
// CSS da:
nav { background: #1a1a2e; }
nav ul { list-style: none; }
nav ul li { display: inline-block; }
nav ul li a { color: white; }
nav ul li a:hover { color: #6c63ff; }

// SCSS da:
nav {
  background: #1a1a2e;

  ul {
    list-style: none;
    display: flex;
    gap: 24px;

    li {
      display: inline-block;

      a {
        color: white;
        text-decoration: none;
        transition: color 0.2s;

        &:hover { color: #6c63ff; } // & = ota element
        &:active { opacity: 0.8; }
        &.active { font-weight: bold; border-bottom: 2px solid #6c63ff; }
      }
    }
  }
}
```

## O'zgaruvchilar
```scss
// SCSS o'zgaruvchilari (compile vaqtida hisob-kitob)
$primary: #6c63ff;
$secondary: #ff6b6b;
$dark-bg: #0f0f1a;
$card-bg: #1a1a2e;
$text: #e0e0e0;

$spacing: 16px;
$radius: 8px;

// Ishlatish
.button {
  background: $primary;
  padding: $spacing $spacing * 2;
  border-radius: $radius;

  &:hover { background: darken($primary, 10%); } // SCSS funksiya
}
```

**SCSS vs CSS o'zgaruvchilari farqi:**
- SCSS `$var` — compile vaqtida hisob-kitob, runtime da o'zgartirib bo'lmaydi
- CSS `--var` — browser da ishlaydi, JavaScript bilan o'zgartirsa bo'ladi

## @mixin va @include

Qayta ishlatiladigan kodni mixin sifatida aniqlash:
```scss
// Mixin aniqlash
@mixin flex-center {
  display: flex;
  justify-content: center;
  align-items: center;
}

@mixin button-style($bg, $color: white) { // Default qiymat
  background: $bg;
  color: $color;
  padding: 12px 24px;
  border: none;
  border-radius: 8px;
  cursor: pointer;
  transition: all 0.2s;

  &:hover { background: darken($bg, 10%); transform: translateY(-2px); }
}

@mixin responsive($breakpoint) {
  @if $breakpoint == mobile {
    @media (max-width: 576px) { @content; }
  } @else if $breakpoint == tablet {
    @media (max-width: 768px) { @content; }
  } @else if $breakpoint == desktop {
    @media (min-width: 992px) { @content; }
  }
}

// Ishlatish
.hero { @include flex-center; min-height: 100vh; }
.btn-primary { @include button-style(#6c63ff); }
.btn-danger { @include button-style(#ff6b6b); }

.card {
  padding: 24px;

  @include responsive(mobile) { padding: 16px; font-size: 14px; }
  @include responsive(tablet) { padding: 20px; }
}
```

## @extend — Uslublarni meros qilish
```scss
// Asosiy klass
%btn-base { // % — placeholder, CSS ga chiqmaydi
  padding: 12px 24px;
  border: none;
  border-radius: 8px;
  cursor: pointer;
  font-size: 16px;
  transition: all 0.2s;
}

.btn-primary {
  @extend %btn-base;
  background: #6c63ff;
  color: white;
}

.btn-outline {
  @extend %btn-base;
  background: transparent;
  border: 2px solid #6c63ff;
  color: #6c63ff;
}
```

**@mixin vs @extend:**
- @mixin — parametr qabul qiladi, har joyga alohida nusxa qo'shadi
- @extend — nusxa qo'shmaydi, selectorlarni birlashtiradi (kichikroq CSS)

## @import va @use (zamonaviy)
```scss
// Eski usul
@import 'variables';
@import 'mixins';
@import 'components/buttons';

// Yangi usul (@use namespace bilan)
@use 'sass:math';
@use 'variables' as v;
@use 'mixins' as m;

.btn { background: v.$primary; }
.card { @include m.flex-center; }
```

## SCSS Funksiyalari
```scss
$base: #6c63ff;

.color-demo {
  background: lighten($base, 20%);  // Ochroq
  border-color: darken($base, 15%); // To'qroq
  color: desaturate($base, 30%);    // Rangsizroq
  outline: transparentize($base, 0.5); // 50% shaffof
}

// math
.grid-item {
  width: math.percentage(1/3); // 33.33%
  margin: math.round(16.7px);  // 17px
}
```

## @each va @for — Loops
```scss
$colors: (primary: #6c63ff, danger: #ff6b6b, success: #51cf66);

@each $name, $color in $colors {
  .btn-#{$name} { background: $color; } // Interpolatsiya
}

// Natija:
// .btn-primary { background: #6c63ff; }
// .btn-danger { background: #ff6b6b; }

@for $i from 1 through 4 {
  .col-#{$i} { width: 25% * $i; }
}
```

## Fayl tuzilishi — 7-1 Pattern
```
scss/
├── abstracts/    # variables, mixins, functions
├── base/         # reset, typography
├── components/   # buttons, cards, forms
├── layout/       # header, footer, grid
├── pages/        # home, about, contact
├── themes/       # dark, light
└── main.scss     # barcha fayllarni import qiladi
```

