nazariya:
Zamonaviy web ilovalar serverdan ma'lumot oladi va yuboradi — sahifani qayta yuklamasdan. Bu asinxron dasturlash orqali amalga oshiriladi.

**Sinxron vs Asinxron**
```javascript
// Sinxron — bir-birini kutadi
console.log('1');
console.log('2');  // 1 tugaguncha kutadi
console.log('3');

// Asinxron — kutmasdan davom etadi
console.log('1');
setTimeout(() => console.log('2'), 1000);
console.log('3');  // Natija: 1, 3, 2
```

**Promise**
Asinxron amalning kelajakdagi natijasini ifodalaydi:
```javascript
const vaad = new Promise((hal_qil, rad_et) => {
  setTimeout(() => {
    const muvaffaqiyatmi = true;
    if (muvaffaqiyatmi) hal_qil('Ma\'lumot tayyor!');
    else rad_et(new Error('Xato yuz berdi'));
  }, 1000);
});

vaad
  .then(natija => console.log(natija))
  .catch(xato => console.error(xato))
  .finally(() => console.log('Har holda bajariladi'));
```

**async/await**
Promise ni yanada o'qilishi oson tarzda yozish:
```javascript
async function malumotOl() {
  try {
    const javob = await fetch('https://api.example.com/users');
    const data = await javob.json();
    console.log(data);
  } catch (xato) {
    console.error('Xato:', xato.message);
  }
}
```

**Fetch API**
Brauzerga o'rnatilgan HTTP so'rovlar kutubxonasi:
```javascript
// GET so'rov
async function foydalanuvchilarOl() {
  const javob = await fetch('https://jsonplaceholder.typicode.com/users');
  if (!javob.ok) {
    throw new Error(`HTTP xato: ${javob.status}`);
  }
  const foydalanuvchilar = await javob.json();
  return foydalanuvchilar;
}

// POST so'rov
async function yangiYozbosOl(maqola) {
  const javob = await fetch('https://jsonplaceholder.typicode.com/posts', {
    method: 'POST',
    headers: {
      'Content-Type': 'application/json',
    },
    body: JSON.stringify(maqola)
  });
  const yangi = await javob.json();
  return yangi;
}

// PUT va DELETE
async function yangilash(id, malumot) {
  await fetch(`/api/items/${id}`, {
    method: 'PUT',
    headers: { 'Content-Type': 'application/json' },
    body: JSON.stringify(malumot)
  });
}

async function ochirish(id) {
  await fetch(`/api/items/${id}`, { method: 'DELETE' });
}
```

