Vue.js — Evan You tomonidan yaratilgan progressiv JavaScript freymvorki. React ga qaraganda o'rganish osonroq, to'liq fayllar (.vue) tuzilmasi aniq va tartibli.

**Vue fayli tuzilmasi (Single File Component)**
```vue
<!-- Karta.vue -->
<template>
  <!-- Faqat bitta root element (Vue 3 da shart emas) -->
  <div class='karta'>
    <h2>{{ sarlavha }}</h2>
    <p>{{ tavsif }}</p>
  </div>
</template>

<script setup>
// Composition API (Vue 3)
import { ref, computed, onMounted } from 'vue';

const props = defineProps({
  sarlavha: String,
  tavsif: String
});
</script>

<style scoped>
/* scoped — faqat bu komponentga ta'sir qiladi */
.karta { padding: 16px; border-radius: 8px; }
</style>
```

**Direktivlar**
```vue
<template>
  <!-- v-bind — atributni bog'lash, :ning qisqartmasi -->
  <img :src='rasm' :alt='nom' />
  <button :disabled='yuklanmoqda'>Yuborish</button>

  <!-- v-on — event tinglash, @ning qisqartmasi -->
  <button @click='saqlash'>Saqlash</button>
  <input @input='qidirish' @keyup.enter='yubor' />

  <!-- v-model — ikki tomonlama bog'lash -->
  <input v-model='ism' />
  <textarea v-model='matn' />
  <input type='checkbox' v-model='rozilik' />
  <select v-model='tanlangan'>
    <option value='python'>Python</option>
    <option value='web'>Web</option>
  </select>

  <!-- v-if / v-else-if / v-else -->
  <div v-if='rol === "admin"'>Admin paneli</div>
  <div v-else-if='rol === "usoz"'>Ustoz paneli</div>
  <div v-else>Talaba paneli</div>

  <!-- v-show — display:none bilan yashiradi (DOM da qoladi) -->
  <div v-show='korinsin'>Men ko'rinayin/ko'rinmayin</div>

  <!-- v-for — ro'yxat -->
  <li v-for='(kurs, indeks) in kurslar' :key='kurs.id'>
    {{ indeks + 1 }}. {{ kurs.nom }}
  </li>

  <!-- v-for ob'ekt ustida -->
  <li v-for='(qiymat, kalit) in sozlamalar' :key='kalit'>
    {{ kalit }}: {{ qiymat }}
  </li>
</template>
```

**Composition API — ref va reactive**
```vue
<script setup>
import { ref, reactive, computed, watch, onMounted, onUnmounted } from 'vue';

// ref — oddiy qiymatlar uchun (template da .value avtomatik)
const hisoblagich = ref(0);
const ism = ref('');

// reactive — ob'ektlar uchun
const holat = reactive({
  yuklanmoqda: false,
  foydalanuvchilar: [],
  xato: null
});

// computed — bog'liq qiymat
const ikkilamchi = computed(() => hisoblagich.value * 2);
const filterlangan = computed(() =>
  holat.foydalanuvchilar.filter(f => f.ism.includes(ism.value))
);

// watch — o'zgarishlarni kuzatish
watch(ism, (yangi, eski) => {
  console.log(`${eski} -> ${yangi}`);
});

watch(() => holat.yuklanmoqda, (yangi) => {
  document.title = yangi ? 'Yuklanmoqda...' : 'SYNAPSE';
});

// Lifecycle
onMounted(async () => {
  holat.yuklanmoqda = true;
  const javob = await fetch('/api/foydalanuvchilar');
  holat.foydalanuvchilar = await javob.json();
  holat.yuklanmoqda = false;
});

onUnmounted(() => {
  console.log('Komponent olib tashlandi');
});

// Metodlar — oddiy funksiyalar
function qosh() {
  hisoblagich.value++;
}

// defineEmits — voqealarni otaga yuborish
const emit = defineEmits(['saqlandi', 'bekor']);
function saqlash() {
  emit('saqlandi', { ism: ism.value });
}
</script>
```

**Props va Emits**
```vue
<!-- Ota -->
<FoydalanuvchiKarta
  :foydalanuvchi='joriyFoydalanuvchi'
  @yangilandi='foydalanuvchiYangilandi'
/>

<!-- Bola -->
<script setup>
const props = defineProps({
  foydalanuvchi: {
    type: Object,
    required: true
  }
});
const emit = defineEmits(['yangilandi']);
function yangilash() {
  emit('yangilandi', { ...props.foydalanuvchi, yangilangan: true });
}
</script>
```

Next.js — Vercel tomonidan yaratilgan React asosidagi full-stack freymvork. Odatiy React da faqat CSR (Client Side Rendering) bor — Next.js SSR va SSG ni ham qo'shadi.

**Rendering turlari**
| Tur | Qachon | Afzallik |
|-----|--------|----------|
| CSR | Brauzerda | Interaktivlik |
| SSR | Har so'rovda server | Aktual ma'lumot, SEO |
| SSG | Build vaqtida | Tezlik, CDN |
| ISR | Fon yangilanishi | SSG + yangilik |

**App Router (Next.js 13+)**
```
app/
├── layout.tsx          # Root layout
├── page.tsx            # /
├── loading.tsx         # Yuklanish
├── error.tsx           # Xato
├── not-found.tsx       # 404
├── kurslar/
│   ├── page.tsx        # /kurslar
│   └── [id]/
│       └── page.tsx    # /kurslar/123
└── api/
    └── foydalanuvchilar/
        └── route.ts    # /api/foydalanuvchilar
```

**Server Components (standart)**
```tsx
// app/kurslar/page.tsx — Server Component
// async ishlaydi, to'g'ridan-to'g'ri DB dan ma'lumot olishi mumkin

async function KurslarSahifasi() {
  // Server tomonida ishlaydi — API key xavfsiz
  const kurslar = await fetch('https://api.example.com/kurslar', {
    cache: 'force-cache'  // SSG
    // cache: 'no-store'  // SSR
    // next: { revalidate: 60 } // ISR
  }).then(r => r.json());

  return (
    <main>
      <h1>Kurslar</h1>
      {kurslar.map(k => (
        <KursKarta key={k.id} kurs={k} />) // Server component
      )}
    </main>
  );
}

export default KurslarSahifasi;

// Metadata
export const metadata = {
  title: 'Kurslar | SYNAPSE',
  description: 'Barcha dasturlash kurslari'
};
```

