**Webpack vs Vite taqqoslash:**
| Xususiyat | Webpack | Vite |
|-----------|---------|------|
| Dev server start | 10-60 sekund | < 1 sekund |
| HMR tezligi | O'rtacha | Tezkor |
| Konfiguratsiya | Murakkab | Sodda |
| Ecosystem | Katta | O'sib bormoqda |
| Production build | Yaxshi | Rollup (yaxshi) |

**Tree-shaking misoli:**
```javascript
// lodash'dan faqat kerakli funksiyani import qilish
import debounce from 'lodash/debounce';     // to'g'ri — faqat 1 funksiya
import { debounce } from 'lodash';           // import o'zi tree-shakeable
import _ from 'lodash';                      // YOMON — butun lodash bundle'ga
```

