Testing — professional frontend dasturlashning muhim qismi. Testlar kodingiz kutilganidek ishlashini ta'minlaydi, refactoring'ni xavfsiz qiladi va regression (avval ishlagan narsaning buzilishini) oldini oladi.

**Test turlari:**
- **Unit test:** bir funksiya yoki komponent alohida sinovdan o'tkaziladi
- **Integration test:** bir nechta komponent birgalikda ishlashi tekshiriladi
- **E2E (End-to-End) test:** foydalanuvchi brauzerda bajariladigan to'liq stsenariy (Playwright, Cypress)

**Jest — eng mashhur test framework:**
```bash
npm install --save-dev jest @babel/preset-env babel-jest
```

```javascript
// utils/math.js
export const sum = (a, b) => a + b;
export const multiply = (a, b) => a * b;
export const divide = (a, b) => {
  if (b === 0) throw new Error('Nolga bo\'lish mumkin emas');
  return a / b;
};

// utils/math.test.js
import { sum, multiply, divide } from './math';

describe('Math utils', () => {
  test('ikki sonni qo\'shadi', () => {
    expect(sum(2, 3)).toBe(5);
    expect(sum(-1, 1)).toBe(0);
  });

  test('ikki sonni ko\'paytiradi', () => {
    expect(multiply(3, 4)).toBe(12);
  });

  test('nolga bo\'lishda xato chiqaradi', () => {
    expect(() => divide(10, 0)).toThrow('Nolga bo\'lish mumkin emas');
  });
});
```

