nazariya:
GraphQL — Meta (Facebook) tomonidan 2015-yilda ochiq manbaga chiqarilgan API query tili. REST API'ning cheklovlarini hal qiladi: over-fetching (kerakdan ko'p ma'lumot) va under-fetching (kerakdan kam ma'lumot) muammolarini bartaraf etadi.

**REST vs GraphQL:**
```
REST — bir nechta endpoint:
GET /users/1           → { id, name, email, address, phone, ... }
GET /users/1/posts     → [{ id, title, body, comments, ... }]
GET /posts/5/comments  → [{ id, text, author, ... }]

GraphQL — bitta endpoint, aniq so'rov:
POST /graphql
{
  user(id: 1) {
    name
    email
    posts {
      title
      comments { text }
    }
  }
}
```

**GraphQL asosiy tushunchalar:**

**1. Schema — tizim tavsifi:**
```graphql
# GraphQL Schema Definition Language (SDL)
type User {
  id: ID!
  name: String!
  email: String!
  age: Int
  posts: [Post!]!
}

type Post {
  id: ID!
  title: String!
  body: String!
  author: User!
  comments: [Comment!]!
  createdAt: String!
}

type Comment {
  id: ID!
  text: String!
  author: User!
}

# ! — null bo'lmasligi
# [Post!]! — bo'sh bo'lmagan post massivi
```

**2. Query — ma'lumot olish:**
```graphql
# Oddiy query
query GetUser {
  user(id: "1") {
    name
    email
    posts {
      title
    }
  }
}

# Variables bilan
query GetUser($userId: ID!) {
  user(id: $userId) {
    name
    email
    age
  }
}
# Variables: { "userId": "1" }

# Bir nechta query (batching)
query Dashboard {
  currentUser {
    name
    notifications { count }
  }
  featuredPosts(limit: 5) {
    title
    author { name }
  }
}

# Fragment — qayta ishlatiladigan field guruhi
fragment UserBasic on User {
  id
  name
  email
}

query Users {
  allUsers {
    ...UserBasic
    posts { title }
  }
}
```

**3. Mutation — ma'lumot o'zgartirish:**
```graphql
# Yangi post yaratish
mutation CreatePost($input: CreatePostInput!) {
  createPost(input: $input) {
    id
    title
    author { name }
    createdAt
  }
}
# Variables:
# {
#   "input": {
#     "title": "GraphQL darsi",
#     "body": "Bu juda foydali texnologiya"
#   }
# }

# Yangilash
mutation UpdateUser($id: ID!, $name: String!) {
  updateUser(id: $id, name: $name) {
    id
    name
  }
}

# O'chirish
mutation DeletePost($id: ID!) {
  deletePost(id: $id) {
    success
    message
  }
}
```

**4. Subscription — real-time:**
```graphql
subscription OnNewMessage($chatId: ID!) {
  messageAdded(chatId: $chatId) {
    text
    author { name }
    createdAt
  }
}
```

