Web xavfsizligi — har bir frontend dasturchining bilishi shart bo'lgan soha. Uchta eng keng tarqalgan hujum turi va ulardan himoya:

**1. XSS — Cross-Site Scripting**
Attacker foydalanuvchi brauzerida zararli JavaScript kodni bajaradi.

```javascript
// XAVFLI — XSS ga moyil kod
const userInput = '<script>document.cookie</script>';
document.getElementById('output').innerHTML = userInput; // XAVFLI!

// XAVFSIZ — textContent ishlatish
document.getElementById('output').textContent = userInput; // Xavfsiz

// XAVFSIZ — escaping funksiyasi
function escapeHtml(text) {
  const div = document.createElement('div');
  div.appendChild(document.createTextNode(text));
  return div.innerHTML;
}

// XAVFSIZ — DOMPurify kutubxonasi
import DOMPurify from 'dompurify';
const clean = DOMPurify.sanitize(userInput);
document.getElementById('output').innerHTML = clean;
```

**2. CSRF — Cross-Site Request Forgery**
Attacker foydalanuvchi nomidan so'rovlar yuboradi.

```javascript
// Server side: CSRF token yaratish (Node.js/Express)
const csrf = require('csurf');
app.use(csrf({ cookie: true }));

app.get('/form', (req, res) => {
  res.render('form', { csrfToken: req.csrfToken() });
});

// HTML formada
<form method="POST" action="/submit">
  <input type="hidden" name="_csrf" value="{{ csrfToken }}">
  <!-- boshqa fieldlar -->
</form>

// Fetch bilan
const response = await fetch('/api/transfer', {
  method: 'POST',
  headers: {
    'Content-Type': 'application/json',
    'X-CSRF-Token': document.cookie.match(/csrfToken=([^;]+)/)?.[1]
  },
  body: JSON.stringify({ amount: 100 })
});

// SameSite cookie — CSRF'ga qarshi eng yaxshi himoya
res.cookie('session', token, {
  httpOnly: true,
  secure: true, // faqat HTTPS
  sameSite: 'strict' // yoki 'lax'
});
```

**3. Content Security Policy (CSP)**
Brauzerga qaysi manbalardan resurslar yuklash mumkinligini aytadi:

```http
# HTTP header
Content-Security-Policy: 
  default-src 'self';
  script-src 'self' 'nonce-{RANDOM_NONCE}' https://cdn.trusted.com;
  style-src 'self' 'unsafe-inline' https://fonts.googleapis.com;
  img-src 'self' data: https:;
  font-src 'self' https://fonts.gstatic.com;
  connect-src 'self' https://api.synapse.uz;
  frame-ancestors 'none';
  base-uri 'self';
  form-action 'self';
```

```html
<!-- HTML meta tag orqali (kamroq kuchli) -->
<meta http-equiv="Content-Security-Policy" 
      content="default-src 'self'; script-src 'self';">

<!-- Nonce bilan (eng xavfsiz) -->
<script nonce="abc123random">console.log('bu ruxsat etilgan')</script>
```

**Qo'shimcha xavfsizlik headerlari:**

```javascript
// Express.js da helmet kutubxonasi
const helmet = require('helmet');
app.use(helmet());

// Bu quyidagilarni avtomatik qo'shadi:
// X-Content-Type-Options: nosniff
// X-Frame-Options: DENY
// X-XSS-Protection: 1; mode=block
// Strict-Transport-Security: max-age=31536000
// Referrer-Policy: no-referrer
```

**localStorage vs Cookie xavfsizligi:**
```javascript
// JWT ni localStorage da saqlash — XSS ga moyil
localStorage.setItem('token', jwt); // XAVFLI

// httpOnly cookie — XSS dan himoyalangan
// (JavaScript orqali o'qib bo'lmaydi)
res.cookie('token', jwt, { httpOnly: true, secure: true, sameSite: 'strict' });
```

Xavfsizlik — qatlama himoya tamoyiliga asoslanadi: bitta himoya yetarli emas, bir nechta qatlamni birlashtirish kerak.

