nazariya:
WebAssembly (WASM) — brauzerda native tezlikga yaqin kod bajarish imkonini beradigan binary format. JavaScript bilan parallel ishlaydi, uni almashtirmaydi.

**WASM nimaga kerak?**
- Video/audio kodek
- 3D grafika va o'yinlar
- Kriptografiya
- AI inference (brauzerda ML)
- Rasm/PDF qayta ishlash
- Murakkab hisob-kitoblar

**C dan WASM** — Emscripten bilan:

```c
// math.c
#include <emscripten/emscripten.h>

EMSCRIPTEN_KEEPALIVE
int add(int a, int b) {
    return a + b;
}

EMSCRIPTEN_KEEPALIVE
double fibonacci(int n) {
    if (n <= 1) return n;
    return fibonacci(n-1) + fibonacci(n-2);
}

// Compile:
// emcc math.c -o math.wasm -s EXPORTED_FUNCTIONS='["_add","_fibonacci"]'
```

```javascript
// JavaScript'da WASM yuklash
async function loadWasm() {
  const response = await fetch('/math.wasm');
  const bytes = await response.arrayBuffer();
  const { instance } = await WebAssembly.instantiate(bytes, {});

  const { add, fibonacci } = instance.exports;
  console.log(add(5, 3));       // 8
  console.log(fibonacci(40));   // tez!
  return instance.exports;
}
```

**Rust dan WASM** — wasm-bindgen bilan (eng zamonaviy yondashuv):

```toml
# Cargo.toml
[package]
name = "wasm-synapse"
version = "0.1.0"
edition = "2021"

[lib]
crate-type = ["cdylib"]

[dependencies]
wasm-bindgen = "0.2"
```

```rust
// src/lib.rs
use wasm_bindgen::prelude::*;

#[wasm_bindgen]
pub fn greet(name: &str) -> String {
    format!("Salom, {}! WASM'dan salom!", name)
}

#[wasm_bindgen]
pub fn calculate_xp(lessons: u32, streak: u32, difficulty: u32) -> u32 {
    let base = lessons * 10;
    let streak_bonus = if streak > 7 { streak * 5 } else { streak * 2 };
    let difficulty_multiplier = match difficulty {
        1 => 100,
        2 => 150,
        3 => 200,
        _ => 100,
    };
    (base + streak_bonus) * difficulty_multiplier / 100
}

#[wasm_bindgen]
pub struct Matrix {
    data: Vec<f64>,
    rows: usize,
    cols: usize,
}

#[wasm_bindgen]
impl Matrix {
    pub fn new(rows: usize, cols: usize) -> Matrix {
        Matrix { data: vec![0.0; rows * cols], rows, cols }
    }

    pub fn set(&mut self, row: usize, col: usize, value: f64) {
        self.data[row * self.cols + col] = value;
    }

    pub fn multiply_scalar(&self, scalar: f64) -> Vec<f64> {
        self.data.iter().map(|x| x * scalar).collect()
    }
}

// Compile:
// wasm-pack build --target web
```

```javascript
// JavaScript'da Rust WASM ishlatish
import init, { greet, calculate_xp, Matrix } from './pkg/wasm_synapse.js';

async function main() {
  await init(); // WASM yukla

  console.log(greet('Mukhammad'));
  // "Salom, Mukhammad! WASM'dan salom!"

  const xp = calculate_xp(5, 10, 2);
  console.log(`XP: ${xp}`);

  const matrix = Matrix.new(3, 3);
  matrix.set(0, 0, 1.5);
  const result = matrix.multiply_scalar(2.0);
  console.log(result);
}

main();
```

**Performance taqqoslama:**
```javascript
// Fibonacci 40 — benchmark
console.time('JS');
fibonacciJS(40);    // ~1800ms
console.timeEnd('JS');

console.time('WASM');
fibonacciWASM(40);  // ~15ms  (100x tez!)
console.timeEnd('WASM');
```

**WASM vositalar ekotizimi:**
- **wasm-pack** — Rust → WASM (npm package sifatida)
- **Emscripten** — C/C++ → WASM
- **AssemblyScript** — TypeScript sintaksisida WASM yozish
- **Pyodide** — Python → brauzerda (WASM orqali)
- **WASI** — WebAssembly System Interface (server side)

Brauzer support: Chrome 57+, Firefox 52+, Safari 11+, Edge 16+ — barcha zamonaviy brauzerlar qo'llab-quvvatlaydi.

