E-commerce frontend — bu bugungi kunda eng ko'p ishlatiladigan real loyiha turlaridan biri. React yordamida to'liq funktsional savat (cart) tizimi yaratish uchun bir nechta muhim kontseptsiyalarni bilish kerak.

**useState va useReducer bilan Cart boshqaruvi**
Kichik loyihalarda `useState` yetarli, lekin cart kabi murakkab holatlarda `useReducer` ancha qulay:

```jsx
const cartReducer = (state, action) => {
  switch (action.type) {
    case 'ADD_ITEM':
      const exists = state.items.find(i => i.id === action.payload.id);
      if (exists) {
        return {
          ...state,
          items: state.items.map(i =>
            i.id === action.payload.id
              ? { ...i, quantity: i.quantity + 1 }
              : i
          )
        };
      }
      return { ...state, items: [...state.items, { ...action.payload, quantity: 1 }] };
    case 'REMOVE_ITEM':
      return { ...state, items: state.items.filter(i => i.id !== action.payload) };
    case 'UPDATE_QTY':
      return {
        ...state,
        items: state.items.map(i =>
          i.id === action.payload.id ? { ...i, quantity: action.payload.qty } : i
        )
      };
    case 'CLEAR_CART':
      return { ...state, items: [] };
    default:
      return state;
  }
};
```

**Context API bilan Global Cart**
Cart holatini butun ilovaga uzatish uchun Context API ishlatiladi:

```jsx
const CartContext = React.createContext();

export const CartProvider = ({ children }) => {
  const [state, dispatch] = useReducer(cartReducer, { items: [] });

  const totalPrice = state.items.reduce(
    (sum, item) => sum + item.price * item.quantity, 0
  );

  const totalItems = state.items.reduce(
    (sum, item) => sum + item.quantity, 0
  );

  return (
    <CartContext.Provider value={{ state, dispatch, totalPrice, totalItems }}>
      {children}
    </CartContext.Provider>
  );
};

export const useCart = () => React.useContext(CartContext);
```

**Mahsulot kartochkasi komponenti**
```jsx
const ProductCard = ({ product }) => {
  const { dispatch } = useCart();
  return (
    <div className="product-card">
      <img src={product.image} alt={product.name} />
      <h3>{product.name}</h3>
      <p>${product.price}</p>
      <button onClick={() => dispatch({ type: 'ADD_ITEM', payload: product })}>
        Savatga qo'sh
      </button>
    </div>
  );
};
```

**localStorage bilan Persistence**
Foydalanuvchi sahifani yangilasa ham cart saqlanib qolishi kerak:
```jsx
useEffect(() => {
  const saved = localStorage.getItem('cart');
  if (saved) dispatch({ type: 'LOAD', payload: JSON.parse(saved) });
}, []);

useEffect(() => {
  localStorage.setItem('cart', JSON.stringify(state.items));
}, [state.items]);
```

**Filtr va Qidiruv**
Mahsulotlarni kategoriya va narx bo'yicha filtrlash:
```jsx
const filteredProducts = products
  .filter(p => category === 'all' || p.category === category)
  .filter(p => p.name.toLowerCase().includes(search.toLowerCase()))
  .sort((a, b) => sortBy === 'price' ? a.price - b.price : a.name.localeCompare(b.name));
```

E-commerce loyihasida UX juda muhim: loading skeleton, optimistic updates, va tranzaktsiya animatsiyalari foydalanuvchi tajribasini yaxshilaydi. Checkout qadamlarini alohida komponentlarga bo'lish (Cart → Shipping → Payment → Confirmation) clean architecture yaratadi.

