**Optimistic Updates (like tizimi)**
Foydalanuvchi like bosganda server javobini kutmasdan darhol UI'ni yangilash:
```jsx
const [posts, setPosts] = useState(initialPosts);

const handleLike = (postId) => {
  // Optimistic: darhol UI'ni yangilaymiz
  setPosts(prev => prev.map(p =>
    p.id === postId ? { ...p, likes: p.likes + 1, liked: true } : p
  ));

  // Server'ga yuboramiz
  send({ type: 'LIKE', postId });

  // Xatolik bo'lsa rollback (amalda try/catch bilan)
};
```

**Infinite Scroll**
```jsx
const observer = useRef();
const lastPostRef = useCallback(node => {
  if (loading) return;
  if (observer.current) observer.current.disconnect();
  observer.current = new IntersectionObserver(entries => {
    if (entries[0].isIntersecting && hasMore) {
      loadMorePosts();
    }
  });
  if (node) observer.current.observe(node);
}, [loading, hasMore]);
```

