PWA (Progressive Web App) — oddiy veb-saytni mobil ilovadek ishlashga imkon beruvchi texnologiyalar to'plami. Offline ishlash, push notification, va home screen'ga qo'shish imkoniyatlari bilan native app tajribasini beradi.

**PWA uchun 3 asosiy talab**
1. HTTPS (yoki localhost)
2. Web App Manifest (manifest.json)
3. Service Worker

**manifest.json**
```json
{
  "name": "Mening PWA Ilovam",
