nazariya:
React va Vue intervyularida Virtual DOM, lifecycle, hooks, performance optimizatsiyasi, va state management eng ko'p so'raladigan mavzular.

**Virtual DOM nima? (1-5)**
Virtual DOM — real DOM'ning JavaScript ob'ekt (VDOM) ko'rinishidagi nusxasi. React har render'da yangi VDOM yaratadi va eski bilan solishtiradi (diffing/reconciliation). Faqat farqlar real DOM'ga qo'llaniladi.

```
Real DOM yangilash: qimmat (layout reflow, repaint)
VDOM diffing: arzon (xotirada JS ob'ekt solishtirish)
Natija: minimal real DOM operatsiyalari
```

**React Lifecycle va Hooks (6-18)**
```
// Class lifecycle → Hooks ekvivalenti
componentDidMount     → useEffect(() => {}, [])
componentDidUpdate    → useEffect(() => {}, [dep])
componentWillUnmount  → useEffect(() => { return cleanup; }, [])
shouldComponentUpdate → React.memo + useMemo + useCallback
```

```jsx
// useEffect to'liq anatomiyasi
useEffect(() => {
  // componentDidMount + componentDidUpdate
  const subscription = subscribe(props.id);

  return () => {
    // componentWillUnmount + prev effect cleanup
    subscription.unsubscribe();
  };
}, [props.id]); // faqat props.id o'zgarganda qayta ishlaydi
```

**useMemo va useCallback (19-26)**
```jsx
// useMemo: qimmat hisob-kitobni cache'lash
const expensiveResult = useMemo(() => {
  return heavyCalculation(largeArray);
}, [largeArray]); // largeArray o'zgargandagina qayta hisoblanadi

// useCallback: funksiya reference'ni saqlash (child re-render oldini olish)
const handleClick = useCallback((id) => {
  dispatch({ type: 'SELECT', payload: id });
}, [dispatch]); // dispatch o'zgarmasa yangi funksiya yaratilmaydi

// React.memo: props o'zgarmasa component re-render bo'lmaydi
const ChildComponent = React.memo(({ value, onAction }) => {
  return <button onClick={onAction}>{value}</button>;
});
```

**Custom Hooks (27-32)**
```jsx
function useFetch(url) {
  const [data, setData] = useState(null);
  const [loading, setLoading] = useState(true);
  const [error, setError] = useState(null);

  useEffect(() => {
    let cancelled = false;
    setLoading(true);
    fetch(url)
      .then(r => r.json())
      .then(d => { if (!cancelled) setData(d); })
      .catch(e => { if (!cancelled) setError(e.message); })
      .finally(() => { if (!cancelled) setLoading(false); });
    return () => { cancelled = true; }; // cleanup: race condition oldini olish
  }, [url]);

  return { data, loading, error };
}
```

**Vue 3 Composition API (33-42)**
```js
import { ref, computed, watch, onMounted } from 'vue';

export default {
  setup() {
    const count = ref(0); // reaktiv primitiv
    const doubled = computed(() => count.value * 2);

    watch(count, (newVal, oldVal) => {
      console.log(`${oldVal} → ${newVal}`);
    });

    onMounted(() => {
      console.log('Komponent mount qilindi');
    });

    return { count, doubled };
  }
}
```

**React Key va Reconciliation (43-46)**
```jsx
// Noto'g'ri: index'ni key sifatida ishlatish
{items.map((item, i) => <Item key={i} {...item} />)} // ❌

// To'g'ri: unique va stable ID
{items.map(item => <Item key={item.id} {...item} />)} // ✅
